title: Bilevel Planning with Learned Symbolic Abstractions from Interaction Data
collection: publications
date: 2026-03-09
citation: 'Dogangun, F., Kilic, B., Bahar, S., & Ugur, E. (2026). Bilevel Planning with Learned Symbolic Abstractions from Interaction Data. arXiv preprint arXiv:2603.08599.'
paperurl: 'https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.08599'
